                    <p><b>Searching for Drug Monographs</b></p><br />
                    You can search for drug monographs in e-CPS using brand name, generic name, therapeutic class, manufacturer or Drug Identification Number (DIN). The following instructions show you how to search for drug monographs in e-CPS using the General Search feature.
                    <p>&nbsp;</p><br />
                    <p><strong>To use General Search:</strong></p><br />
					
					<p>1. Select your method of search:</p>
					<br/>
			
					<table style="text-align: left; width: 100%;" border="0" cellpadding="2" cellspacing="2">
						
