						<td style="vertical-align: top; width: 9px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
					
						</td>
						
						<tr>
						<td style="vertical-align: top; width: 4px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</td>
						<td style="vertical-align: top; width: 1156px;"><b>Note:</b> for search methods: Brand and Generic, Generic, Therapeutic Class, Manufacturer, and DIN, initial search results appear in the top of two list boxes. For search method Brand, the results appear in one list box: the <b>Select a brand name to display monograph</b> list box.<br>
						</td>
						
                    </table>
						<br>
				
                  
